In late March, we began a pilot test of Free Electric in India. We gave away 25 bikes to homes, schools, and small businesses without power. We wanted to see how the bike worked in real life. The response was amazing.

The Green Microcycle Plus

A true beach cruiser. The 5 level pedal assist (with manual throttle override) keeps you going at an easy pace, and the wheels are fat enough to handle the sand. You couldn't pull this off on a non-motorized bike.
